<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>บริการนักท่องเที่ยว</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kanit:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>body { font-family: 'Kanit', sans-serif; }</style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#F8FAFC] pb-32">

    <header class="bg-indigo-600 px-5 pt-12 pb-20 rounded-b-[40px] shadow-lg relative">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-black text-white italic">SERVICES</h1>
        <p class="text-indigo-100 text-sm">เลือกบริการที่ต้องการสำรวจในบุรีรัมย์</p>
    </header>

    <main class="px-6 -mt-10 relative z-10 mb-10">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            
            <a href="/places" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-[35px] shadow-md border border-indigo-50 flex flex-col items-center text-center active:scale-95 transition-all">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-3">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-gray-800">สถานที่ท่องเที่ยว</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Attractions</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/routes" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-[35px] shadow-md border border-indigo-50 flex flex-col items-center text-center active:scale-95 transition-all">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-3">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-route"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-gray-800">เส้นทางท่องเที่ยว</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Travel Routes</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/activities" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-[35px] shadow-md border border-indigo-50 flex flex-col items-center text-center active:scale-95 transition-all">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-3">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-gray-800">กิจกรรม</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Activities</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/restaurants" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-[35px] shadow-md border border-indigo-50 flex flex-col items-center text-center active:scale-95 transition-all">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-3">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-utensils"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-gray-800">ร้านอาหาร</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Restaurants</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/accommodations" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-[35px] shadow-md border border-indigo-50 flex flex-col items-center text-center active:scale-95 transition-all">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-3">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-bed"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-gray-800">ที่พัก</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Accommodations</span>
            </a>

            <div class="bg-gray-100/50 p-6 rounded-[35px] border border-dashed border-gray-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center opacity-60">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 text-gray-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-bold italic">COMING SOON</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-indigo-900 rounded-[30px] p-6 text-white overflow-hidden relative shadow-xl shadow-indigo-100">
            <div class="relative z-10">
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">ต้องการผู้ช่วยส่วนตัว?</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-indigo-200 leading-relaxed">ถาม "น้องรุ้ง AI" ได้ทุกเรื่องเกี่ยวกับทริปนี้<br>ไม่ว่าจะหาที่กิน ที่เที่ยว หรือของฝาก</p>
                <a href="/chat" class="inline-block mt-4 bg-white text-indigo-900 px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold active:scale-90 transition-transform shadow-md">
                    คุยกับน้องรุ้ง <i class="fa-solid fa-comment-dots ml-1"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-robot absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 text-8xl text-white/10 rotate-12"></i>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/nav') %>
</body>
</html>